import React from "react";
import { Form, Container } from "react-bootstrap";

export default function SignIn() {
  return (
    <>
      <Container className="w-50 mt-5 p-5" style={{background:'#77b'}}>
        <header className="text-center" style={{fontSize:'50px'}}>Sign In!</header>
        <Form className="">
          <Form.Group className="mt-5 d-flex align-items-center flex-column">
            <Form.Label className="align-self-start">Full name</Form.Label>
            <Form.Control type="text" className="w-50"></Form.Control>
          </Form.Group>
          <Form.Group className="mt-5 d-flex align-items-center flex-column">
            <Form.Label className="align-self-start">Email</Form.Label>
            <Form.Control type="email" className="w-50"></Form.Control>
          </Form.Group>
          <Form.Group className="mt-5 d-flex align-items-center flex-column">
            <Form.Label className="align-self-start">Pasword</Form.Label>
            <Form.Control type="password" className="w-50"></Form.Control>
          </Form.Group>
        </Form>
      </Container>
    </>
  );
}
